Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéDia selalu mengantre\N‚Äédan tersenyum bodoh di kasir Yamada.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAku ingat karena dia terlihat\N‚Äéseperti anjing keluargaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéTapi siapa "Tayama"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéApa maksudmu Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKenapa kau mengungkit Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaksudku Tayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia wanita muda, dewasa untuk\N‚Äéorang seusianya, dan pakai jaket keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia bilang dia teman Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéOh. Orang ini dipermainkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéJadi, kau di sini untuk merokok\N‚Äébersama Yama‚Ä¶ Yama‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaksudku, "Tayama" malam ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTidak. Aku hanya ingin\N‚Äémemberikannya sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéApa dia memerasmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéIni hadiah terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéHadiah terima kasih?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTayama akan segera keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéIngin kupanggilkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTidak. Kau tak harus melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAku hanya ingin memberikannya ini\N‚Äéjika dia ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaaf merepotkan, tapi bisakah\N‚Äékau memberikan ini kepadanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia akan tahu ini untuk apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaaf merepotkanmu saat sedang istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéDia benar-benar mirip anjing keluargaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéBeth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéManajer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKenapa kau tak mengajakku\N‚Äéuntuk istirahat merokok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéYamada. Ada yang ingin kubicarakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHah? Apa yang kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau sering merokok di sini\N‚Äébersama pelanggan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAku tak merokok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau pembohong, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéJangan menyembunyikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAku sudah dengar dari Sasaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia ke sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia baru pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTak bisa dipercaya. Aku hampir\N‚Äémelaporkannya karena dia mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia bilang berikan ini\N‚Äékepada "Tayama-san".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKatanya itu hadiah terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéItu kau, 'kan? "Tayama."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTapi kau tak kreatif.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äé"Tayama" dan "Yamada"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéCuma dia yang bisa terkecoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéJangan main-main\N‚Äédengan orang tua baik seperti dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHei, apa kau bahkan mendengarkan‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKubilang itu bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéOh, aku mengerti apa ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéIni jenis hiburan yang bagus\N‚Äéuntuk sif malam yang membosankan‚Ä¶{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAkan kubiarkan untuk sementara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAku pergi buru-buru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéSemoga Tayama-san tak dapat masalah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéJangan undang orang asing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéMaafkan aku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAku menyita hadiahmu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéKau terlalu kejam{\i0}‚Äé‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéKau tak boleh merokok lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéKasihanilah aku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéSiapa sangka plot melon itu\N‚Äémuncul lagi seperti ini?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAku tak sabar membaca volume selanjutnya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéYang mana yang harus kubaca selanjutnya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéOh. Itu kau, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKupikir kau hanya sif malam hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKepala Maezawa kesulitan menyusun jadwal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äéjadi di sinilah aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau catat jam kerjamu dengan benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéYa. Sudah kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHei, Manajer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau sudah tak mengisap\N‚Äérokok biasa lagi, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéYa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéIni lebih diterima masyarakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDan aku bosan menyemprot pewangi\N‚Äédan menyikat gigi setelahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKata orang yang mengajariku itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéJadi? Tak perlu basa-basi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéJika ada yang ingin\N‚Äékau katakan, katakanlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHanya saja‚Ä¶ Aku tak pernah bertanya\N‚Äéapa boleh terus merokok di belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéApa? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaksudmu dengan orang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau tak melaporkannya bukan agar kau bisa\N‚Äé"menyingkirkannya" dengan caramu 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau tak menguburnya di suatu tempat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau ingin pelurunya ditembakkan ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDi mana pun kecuali paru-paru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKenapa aku melakukan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau mungkin tak akan mendengarkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äétapi yang kukatakan hanyalah\N‚Äéjangan "terlalu" mempermainkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äé"Terlalu". Berarti jangan berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKubiarkan karena itu di luar jam kerja\N‚Äédan tak mengganggu tim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTapi jika kau "berlebihan",\N‚Äéaku akan menghentikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSelain itu, tak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTitik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSyukurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHei, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKatakan padaku\N‚Äéjika terjadi sesuatu, paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTentu, tapi‚Ä¶ Apa yang akan terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBukankah sudah jelas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKatakan padaku jika jantungmu\N‚Äéberdebar cepat karena gembira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBaik. Sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAku harus minta maaf padanya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAku hanya ingin berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMemangnya aku siapa,\N‚Äémembuatnya dalam masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTayama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKenapa kau mengendap-endap seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAku bertemu karyawan lain kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau tak dapat masalah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéOh. Kau bertemu manajer toko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéManajer toko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéItu bukan hal besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSelain itu, kemarilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHei, tunggu‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaksudmu manajer toko\N‚Äémembolehkan merokok di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéDia bilang tak masalah\N‚Äéjika tak berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äé"Tak berlebihan‚Ä¶"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéItu tak terdengar seperti diperbolehkan‚Ä¶{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéOh, dan Sasaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBenda ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéIni imut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKatamu kau tak mau uang,\N‚Äétapi aku masih ingin berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAku senang kau suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéYa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHanya melihat ini saja\N‚Äémembuatku tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBenarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKubayangkan kau mempertimbangkan\N‚Äéakan membelikanku apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKenapa itu membuatmu tersenyum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau pasti kesulitan menemukan ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTak mudah menemukan sesuatu\N‚Äéseimut ini di toko akhir-akhir ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéJadi, saat kupikir kau bertanya\N‚Äépada staf toko di mana ini dijual{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚Äédan menuju ke bagian pernak-pernik\N‚Äéyang selalu penuh wanita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚Äémerasa canggung,\N‚Äétapi terus mencari sesuatu untukku‚Ä¶{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTayama-san, kau peramal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMembayangkannya saja membuatku tersenyum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSepertinya kau baru mengejek pria tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéOh? Bukan begitu.\N‚ÄéKau membuatku merasa lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéAku tak tahu dia serius atau bercanda.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTerima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAkan kurawat ini sepenuh hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéYang mana pun tak masalah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéHei, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBukankah sudah waktunya\N‚Äékau buang abu rokokmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBenar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau bisa pakai ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBagus sekali itu bisa\N‚Äélangsung digunakan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTerima ka‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéItu terlalu dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBuang dengan benar,\N‚Äékalau tidak kau kena api.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSilakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéBuang abunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTidak‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau bisa berikan saja padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKalau begitu, ambillah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéApa‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSedikit lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéLagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKenapa kau menjauhkannya dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéLenganmu panjang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéAyolah, Tayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéLenganku akan‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéKoyo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéJangan bilang‚Ä¶{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéKau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéYa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaaf, aku tersedak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéMaafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéYamada-san, tak perlu minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:22:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}‚ÄéKurasa pria tua memang butuh waktu lama\N‚Äéuntuk sembuh dari keseleo otot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSasaki-san, maafkan aku‚Ä¶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTak apa-apa, Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äé- Maafkan aku.\N‚Äé- Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚Äé- Berhenti minta maaf.\N‚Äé- Aku minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéSudah kubilang, tak apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}‚ÄéTerjemahan subtitle oleh Rahayu Kinasih
